title: VA Blues Folk - True Love (Dutch Treat Sweetlist ^C064 XHQ)
description:
Just had enough of that modern stuff. Energy level is very high. To bring it down a bit; some Blues. Fortunately I have a lot to choose from, so I jumped in like Dagobert Duck used to do. And I found some wonderful tracks I would like to play for anybody. It will be hard to find a better line-up of "top" songs and sound..... Enjoy,
